<span class="displaytext">mayor (candidate full) released the following statement on the assassination of former prime minister benazir bhutto: <p>"the assassination of benazir bhutto is a tragic event for pakistan and for democracy in pakistan. her murderers must be brought to justice and pakistan must continue the path back to democracy and the rule of law. her death is a reminder that terrorism anywhere — whether in new york, london, tel-aviv or rawalpindi — is an enemy of freedom. we must redouble our efforts to win the terrorists' war on us."</p></span>



